The City Utilities provides basic styles for building an app in The City. 

Documentation at http://developer.onthecity.org/thecity-appkit.

DEPLOYING TO THE INTERNETZ

From the command line, do the following:

Remove old assets: rake assets:clean
Generate new assets: rake assets:precompile
Start the server: rails s

In a new terminal window, grab the documentation pages for the documentation site. cd to an empty directory anywhere: 
	wget -m localhost:3000 

In thecity-appkit project, change to the github branch that has the docs (gh-pages).

Replace everything in this branch with the files you grabbed with wget.
Commit and Push.

Upload the assets you grabbed with wget, to S3.